\id PHP
\h Ifilippiyen
\toc1 Ifilippiyen
\toc2 Ifilippiyen
\toc3 Fil.
\mt1 Ifilippiyen
\c 1
\s1 Aseǧem ɣar umezwaru d tẓaǧit ak-d uqadi
\m 
\v 1 Bulus d Timutiyu, imsexxaren n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, i marra imqeddasen di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ inni iǧan di Filippi, ak-d imɣaren d imsexxaren \add di tmesmunt\add*:
\v 2 Arḍa ad kiwem yiři, uřa d řehna zi AREBBI Babatneɣ, u zi Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Rum. 1:7; 1 Bṭ. 1:2. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 3 Ttqadiɣ AREBBI inu řami daywem ttfekkareɣ řebda, \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt Afa. 1:15; Kul. 1:3; 1 Ts. 1:2; 2 Ts. 1:3. \x*
\v 4 maɣar di kuř tiẓaǧitin inu xawem, aqa ksiɣ s řmeɛruf s řefraḥet
\v 5 di ssibbet n tmunt nwem ak-d L’Injil, zeg wass amezwaru ař iḍa.
\v 6 Aqa ttiqqeɣ belli Wenni daywem ibdan řexdayem iṣebḥen, ad tent ikemmeř ař ass n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 1:6 \xt Yḥ. 6:29; 1 Ts. 1:3. \x*
\v 7 Icna ayi ad fekkareɣ daywem marra ammu, minzi aqa kenniw ɣari deg wuř inu, xmi ǧiɣ di ssnaseř uřa xmi ɣa awteɣ x tidett n L’Injil, \add minzi\add* kenniw tcarcem akidi di arḍa. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Afa. 3:1; 4:1; Kul. 4:3, 18; 2 Tim. 1:8. \x*
\v 8 Minzi AREBBI d Acehhad inu mecḥař kenniw ttexseɣ s řeḥnunect yuǧɣen n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Rum. 1:9; 9:1; 2 Kur. 1:23; 11:31; Gal. 1:20; 1 Ts. 2:5; 1 Tim. 5:21; 2 Tim. 4:1. \x*
\m 
\v 9 Man aya i ttẓaǧiɣ, aqa tayri nwem ad tfeyyeḍ aṭṭas s waṭṭas di tussna d qaɛ řefhamet taruḥanect,
\v 10 maḥend ad tfarzem min ittřiqen, u maḥend ad tiřim teqqurem u břa řɛib deg wass n Lmasiḥ,
\v 11 teccurem s řɣiǧet n tsegda i yeǧan di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ i uɛuǧi d usemɣar n AREBBI.
\b
\s1 Bulus di řeḥbes
\m 
\v 12 \add A\add* aytma, necc xseɣ ad tessnem belli timesřayin i d ayi imsaren arnint ɛad di tuzzeggart \add n tbarreḥt\add* n L’Injil,
\v 13 minzi tᵉttwassen tmeḥbast inu zi ssibbet n Lmasiḥ i qaɛ inni iǧan di řeqṣar n qayṣar u i qaɛ min iqqimen.
\v 14 Azyen ameqqran n wawmaten di Siditneɣ, umi ǧiɣ di tmeḥbast, idweř ɣarsen ttiqqet ktar uca dewřen zeɛɛmen ssawařen awař n AREBBI s teryast ktar, břa tiggʷudi. \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt Afa. 3:13; 1 Ts. 3:3. \x*
\v 15 Ca \add zzaysen\add* ttbarrḥen Lmasiḥ zi řeḥsed d umɛaned, maca ca nneɣni ɛawed zi nneyyet tecna u s tayri,
\v 16 minzi nitni ssnen aqa ttwaggeɣ maḥend ad wteɣ x L’Injil.
\v 17 Maca inni ittbarrḥen s Lmasiḥ s umɛaned, war t tteggen s nneyyet tecna, maca ttexsen ad xafi arnin řmeḥnet i ssnaseř inu.
\m 
\v 18 S man aya farrheɣ, \add wah,\add* ad farḥeɣ: aqa ittwabarreḥ Lmasiḥ s ibriden ifarzen, ma s ijj n lɣaraḍ nneɣni, niɣ s tidett.
\v 19 Minzi ssneɣ aqa timesřayin-a ad iřint i Tudart i necc s tẓaǧit nwem u s tewhibt n Arruḥ n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, \x ◘ \xo 1:19 \xt Řex. 16:7; 2 Kur. 1:11. \x*
\v 20 maḥend necc, am sitimeɣ u ttrajiɣ, war ttseḍḥiɣ ca x walu, maca am řebda, uřa d řexxu ad ittwassemɣar Lmasiḥ s bṭayṭay di arrimet inu, ma s tudart \add inu\add* niɣ s řmewt \add inu\add*. \x ◘ \xo 1:20 \xt Rum. 5:5. \x*
\v 21 Minzi tudart inu d Lmasiḥ uca řmewt d arbeḥ i necc.
\v 22 Maca mařa din řɣiǧet di tudart-a di arrimet zi jjihet n řxedmet inu, \add xenni\add* war ssineɣ min ɣa xḍareɣ.
\v 23 Maɣar aqa ayi jar tnayen n iɣezdisen: dayi meẓri maḥend ad raḥeɣ ad iřiɣ ak-d Lmasiḥ, minzi man aya qaɛ ḥsen,
\v 24 maca aɣimi di arrimet ittxeṣṣa ɛad ktar di ṭṭweɛ nwem.
\v 25 D man aya ssneɣ nican, aqa ad qqimeɣ, \add wah,\add* ad qqimeɣ di ṭṭweɛ n řefraḥet nwem u maḥend ad igma l’iman nwem,
\v 26 ḥima, xmi dd ɣa yaseɣ ɣarwem ɛawed, aqa asemɣar nwem di Lmasiḥ waha ad ifeyyeḍ, umi necc \add qqimeɣ\add*.
\m 
\v 27 Uyurem s uweqqar i Řexbar Aṣebḥan n Lmasiḥ, ḥima, xmi dd ɣa yaseɣ uca ad kenniw ẓareɣ uřa xmi ɣa ɣabeɣ, ad zzaywem sřeɣ, aqa tbeddem nican deg ijj n arruḥ u s ijj n řeɛmar, uca tᵉttɣellbem s l’iman di L’Injil. \x ◘ \xo 1:27 \xt Amz. 17:1; 1 Kur. 7:20; Afa. 4:1; Kul. 1:10; 1 Ts. 2:12; 4:1. \x*
\v 28 War tteggʷdem ca ɛemmarṣ zeg inni xawem dd-ikkaren. Man aya d aɛeǧem i nitni ɣar uhellek, maca i kenniw ɣar usenjem.
\v 29 Minzi aqa immewc awem zi AREBBI, war iǧi ad tamnem di Lmasiḥ waha, maca ɛawed maḥend ad tmarrtem di ṭṭweɛ nnes,
\v 30 u ad teksim amenɣi, am mammec i d ayi t teẓrim uca řexxu aqa xafi tesřim.
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Awaḍeɛ n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ
\m 
\v 1 Mařa xenni ɣarwem ca n ufewwej di Lmasiḥ, awařen s tayri i wuř, niɣ tamunt n Arruḥ, niɣ řeḥnunect di daxeř d arreḥmet,
\v 2 kemmřem řefraḥet inu umi ɣa imun array nwem, ad ɣarwem tiři tayri d icten, d řeɛmar d ijjen uřa d uxarraṣ d ijjen. \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Rum. 12:16; 15:5; 1 Kur. 1:10; Fil. 3:16; 1 Bṭ. 3:8. \x*
\v 3 War tteggem ca uřa d ict n řḥajjet s umɛaned niɣ zi tuffet ixwan, maca ejj kuř ijj ad iweqqar wenneɣni ktar zeg ixef nnes s uwaḍeɛ. \x ◘ \xo 2:3 \xt Rum. 12:10; 1 Bṭ. 5:5. \x*
\v 4 War ixezzar uřa d ijj ɣar ixef nnes waha, maca ejj kuř ijj ad ixzar ɛawed ɣar wenni d as yudsen. \x ◘ \xo 2:4 \xt 1 Kur. 10:24; 13:5. \x*
\v 5 Ejj ad daywem tiři nneyyet i tuɣa ɛawed di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt Mt. 11:29; Yḥ. 13:15; 1 Bṭ. 2:21; 1 Yḥ. 2:6. \x*
\v 6 wenni, am iǧa deg warwas n AREBBI, war iḥsib ca d takeccaḍt umi imqudda ak-d AREBBI, \x ◘ \xo 2:6 \xt 2 Kur. 4:4; Kul. 1:15; Ɛbr. 1:3. \x*
\v 7 maca issexwa Ixef nnes, iksi ṣṣifet n umsexxar. Netta idweř deg warwas n bnadem, uca ittwaf di furma n bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 2:7 \xt Izhd. 8:6; Mt. 20:28; Yḥ. 13:14. \x*
\v 8 Netta isswaḍeɛ Ixef nnes uca idweř iṭṭaɛ ař řmewt, \add wah,\add* ař řmewt n ṣṣalib. \x ◘ \xo 2:8 \xt Ɛbr. 2:9, 14, 17; 4:15; 12:2. \x*
\v 9 S uya issuɛřa i-t AREBBI qaɛ sennej uca iwca as Isem sennej i kuř isem, \x ◘ \xo 2:9 \xt Řex. 2:33; Ɛbr. 1:4. \x*
\v 10 ḥima deg Yisem n Yasuɛ ad aḍaren marra ifadden nni iǧan deg ujenna u x temmurt u sadu temmurt, \x ◘ \xo 2:10 \xt Ica. 45:23; Rum. 14:11. \x*
\v 11 u \add ḥima\add* ad iched kuř iřes belli Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ d SIDI i uɛuǧi n AREBBI, Babas. \x ◘ \xo 2:11 \xt Yḥ. 13:13; 1 Kur. 8:6; 12:3. \x*
\b
\s1 Tifawin di ddunect
\m 
\v 12 S uyenni, \add a\add* imɛizzen inu, am mammec tuɣa tᵉṭṭaɛem řebda, war iǧi xmi akidwem ǧiɣ waha, řexxu ɛad ktar xmi xawem i ɣa aggʷjeɣ, xedmem s ufeyyeḍ i Tudart nwem s tiggʷudi d tarjijat,
\v 13 minzi AREBBI d wenni daywem ixeddmen ař ɣa texsem u ad teggem min di tᵉmmeẓřem kenniw. \x ◘ \xo 2:13 \xt 2 Kur. 3:5. \x*
\v 14 Ggem marra břa řeɛkaset u břa amcubbec, \x ◘ \xo 2:14 \xt Rum. 12:17; 1 Bṭ. 2:12; 4:9. \x*
\v 15 ḥima ad tiřim břa řɛib, am tarwa imezdagen n AREBBI inni izeddɣen di řwesṭ n jjiř iɛewwjen d ifarɣen, u \add ḥima\add* ad tbanem jar asen am tfawin di ddunect, \x ◘ \xo 2:15 \xt Awřn. 4:18; Mt. 5:14. \x*
\v 16 maḥend ad tiřim di ṭṭweɛ nsen deg wemcan n Tudart, ḥima ad ɣari yiři usemɣar deg wass n Lmasiḥ, war uyureɣ baṭeř niɣ xedmeɣ s walu. \x ◘ \xo 2:16 \xt 2 Kur. 1:14; 1 Ts. 2:19. \x*
\v 17 Maca mařa ttᵉttwarucceɣ am yict n tewhibt \add n useyyeb\add* x tɣarṣt u x tsexxart di ṭṭweɛ n l’iman nwem, ad farḥeɣ ɛawed uca ad arecqeɣ akidwem marra. \x ◘ \xo 2:17 \xt 2 Kur. 7:4. \x*
\v 18 \add Xenni uřa d kenniw,\add* farḥem uca farḥem ɛawed akidi.
\b
\s1 Timutiyu d Ipafruditus
\m 
\v 19 Maca necc ssitimeɣ di Siditneɣ Yasuɛ ad awem dd-ssekkeɣ Timutiyu deɣya, ḥima ad iřiɣ x řxaḍar inu xmi ɣa ssneɣ ameddur nwem. \x ◘ \xo 2:19 \xt Řex. 16:1; Rum. 16:21; 1 Ts. 3:2. \x*
\v 20 Minzi war ɣari danita uřa d ijjen am necc, wenni ikessin s wemnus x mammec iffeɣ umeddur nwem s cḍaret.
\v 21 Minzi marra yarezzun di min nsen, war iǧi di min iǧan n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 2:21 \xt 1 Kur. 10:24; 13:5. \x*
\v 22 Maca kenniw tessnem taqeǧebt nnes, belli tuɣa ixeddem akidi di \add tbarreḥt n\add* Řexbar Aṣebḥan am yijj n mmis ɣar babas.
\v 23 Necc ssitimeɣ ad ɣarwem t-i-dd-ssekkeɣ deɣya, xmi ɣa ẓareɣ mammec ɣa iffeɣ umeddur inu.
\v 24 Maca ttiqqeɣ di Sidi inu, belli ɛawed necc ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ deɣya.
\m 
\v 25 Maca ittɣiř ayi belli tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad dd-awem ssekkeɣ uma Ipafruditus, wenni d amɛawen inu d amsexxar akidi, maca netta \add ɛawed\add* d rrasul nwem d amsexxar nwem di min ḥdajeɣ. \f ◼ \fr 2:25 \fk rrasul\ft - niɣ ‘amazan’.\f*
\v 26 Minzi tuɣa iweḥḥec aṭṭas ad kenniw iẓar marra, uca tuɣa iksi s wemnus minzi kenniw tesřim belli tuɣa ihřec.
\v 27 S tidett, tuɣa ihřec ař řmewt, maca AREBBI tuɣa yarḥem i-t, war iǧi netta waha, aḥeqqa uřa d necc, ḥima war ɣari ittiři ufeqquṣ x ufeqquṣ.
\v 28 S uyenni ssekkeɣ t s tazřa aṭṭas, ḥima, xmi t ɣa tẓarem ɛawed, ad tfarḥem uca ad dayi yiři drus n wemnus.
\v 29 S uyenni qebřem t di SIDI, s marra řefraḥet, weqqarem inni iǧan am wanita, \x ◘ \xo 2:29 \xt 1 Kur. 9:14; Gal. 6:6; 1 Ts. 5:12; 1 Tim. 5:17; Ɛbr. 13:17. \x*
\v 30 minzi x ssibbet n řxedmet n Lmasiḥ, tuɣa iqarreb ɣar řmewt am isebbeř tudart n yixef nnes, maḥend ad ikemmeř min ineqṣen di tsexxart nwem i necc.
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Aḍfar n uřaɣi n Arebbi
\m 
\v 1 S uyenni, \add a\add* aytma, farḥem di Siditneɣ. War xafi yewɛar ad awem ariɣ timesřayin-a twařa nneɣnit, minzi ad zzaysent tᵉttwaḥḍam. \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt Fil. 4:4; Yaɛ. 1:2; 1 Bṭ. 4:13. \x*
\m 
\v 2 Ḥḍam ixef nwem zeg yiṭan, ḥḍam zeg ixeddamen iɛeffanen, ḥḍam zeg inni iqeṭṭɛen aysum. \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt Ica. 56:10. \x*
\v 3 Minzi neccin d axtan, \add neccin\add* inni ittsexxaren i AREBBI s Arruḥ, inni issemɣaran di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, uca war ttiqqen ca deg \add wextan n\add* weysum \add n bnadem\add*. \x ◘ \xo 3:3 \xt Aɛwd. 10:16; 30:6; Irm. 4:4; Yḥ. 4:24; Rum. 2:29; Kul. 2:11. \x*
\m 
\v 4 Necc zemmareɣ ad ttiqqeɣ deg weysum \add inu\add*, minzi mařa ittɣiř i ḥed ad ittiqq deg weysum \add nnes\add*, necc ktar: \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt 2 Kur. 11:21. \x*
\v 5 aqa ayi d amextan zeg wami ɣari tmenya n wussan, zi řgens n Israil, zeg ayt n Binyamin, necc d Aɛibrani zeg Iɛibraniyyen, zi jjihet n Ccariɛa necc d Afarisi, \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Amz. 49:27; Lawi 12:3; Řex. 23:6; 2 Kur. 11:22. \x*
\v 6 zeg uɣezdis n cḍaret tuɣa darrceɣ x tmesmunt \add n Lmasiḥ\add*, zeg uɣezdis n tsegda tenni di Ccariɛa aqa ayi břa řɛib. \x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Řex. 8:3; 9:1; 22:3, 4; Gal. 1:13; 1 Tim. 1:13. \x*
\v 7 Maca min tuɣa ɣari arbeḥ, aqa ggiɣ t d taxessart x ssibbet n Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 3:7 \xt Mt. 13:44. \x*
\v 8 Necc ggiɣ marra man aya d taxessart zi ssibbet n tussna n Sidi Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, wenni di ṭṭweɛ nnes xsareɣ kuřci, ggiɣ t amecnaw wefraḍ yurṣuḍen ḥima ad arebḥeɣ Lmasiḥ, \x ◘ \xo 3:8 \xt Ica. 53:11; Irm. 9:22; Yḥ. 17:3; Kul. 2:2. \x*
\v 9 maḥend ad ttwafeɣ dayes, war iǧi s tsegda n ixef inu tenni zi Ccariɛa - maca ak-d tenni dd-itteffɣen zi l’iman n Lmasiḥ, aqa-tt d tasegda tenni zi AREBBI - \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt Rum. 1:17; 3:21. \x*
\v 10 ḥima ammu i ɣa ssneɣ Yasuɛ d jjehd n tnukra nnes, u \add maḥend\add* ad carceɣ deg uweddeb nnes, ad dewřeɣ deg warwas n řmewt nnes, \x ◘ \xo 3:10 \xt Rum. 8:17; 2 Kur. 4:10; 2 Tim. 2:11, 12; 1 Bṭ. 4:13. \x*
\v 11 ḥima s ca n webrid ad awḍeɣ ɣar tnukra zi taddart n imettinen.
\m 
\v 12 Necc war ttiwiḍeɣ niɣ ttwakemmřeɣ ɛad, maca yemmareɣ i man aya, ḥima, mařa iɛeddeř, ad ṭṭfeɣ min xef i d ayi iṭṭef Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.
\v 13 \add A\add* aytma, war d ayi ittɣiř aqa ṭṭfeɣ t, maca tteggeɣ ict n řḥajjet: ttuɣ min awarni ayi uca ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ ixef inu ɣar min din zzati.
\v 14 Ttizzareɣ ɣar lɣaraḍ ḥima ad ṭṭfeɣ \add ttaj n\add* uɣelleb n třaɣit yuɛřan n AREBBI tenni iǧan di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 3:14 \xt 1 Kur. 9:24; 2 Tim. 4:7. \x*
\m 
\v 15 Ejj inni iwḍen ɣar řekmaret, ad rekkzen xenni di tmesřayin-a. Uca mařa ɣarwem nneyyet nneɣni di ca, aqa AREBBI ad awem isscen man aya ɛawed.
\v 16 Maca ejj aneɣ, ḥima ad naweḍ ɣar man aya, ad nuyur deg webrid d ijjen s ixariṣṣen nneɣ d ijjen. \x ◘ \xo 3:16 \xt Rum. 12:16; 15:5; 1 Kur. 1:10; Gal. 6:16; Fil. 2:2; 1 Bṭ. 3:8. \x*
\v 17 Ḍfarem ayi-dd, \add a\add* aytma, ksim tiweṣṣaf i inni yuyuren ɛlaḥsab amedya i zzayneɣ teẓrim. \x ◘ \xo 3:17 \xt 1 Kur. 4:16; 11:1; 1 Ts. 1:6. \x*
\v 18 Minzi aqa din aṭṭas inni yuyuren war iǧi amenni, nniɣ awem tt aṭṭas n imuren - uca řexxu ad tt iniɣ s imeṭṭawen - aqa aten d řɛedyan n ṣṣalib n Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 3:18 \xt Rum. 16:17. \x*
\v 19 Aneggaru nsen d ahellek, arebbi nsen d aɛeddis nsen uca aɛuǧi nsen d abehdeř nsen, u nneyyet nsen di tmesřayin n ddunect.
\v 20 Maca neccin nᵉttsexxar deg ijenwan i zzayes nettraja ɛawed wenni d aneɣ itticen Tudart, Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, \x ◘ \xo 3:20 \xt 1 Kur. 1:7; 1 Ts. 1:10; Tit. 2:13; Ɛbr. 13:14. \x*
\v 21 wenni i ɣa ibeddřen arrimet nneɣ iḥebḍen, ḥima ad tedweř di ṣṣifet n Arrimet nnes iɛuǧen, ɛlaḥsab jjehd nnes tameqqrant i zi i ɣa ittwagg marra min iǧan swadday Nnes. \x ◘ \xo 3:21 \xt 1 Kur. 15:51; Kul. 3:4; 1 Yḥ. 3:2. \x*
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Awař d useǧem aneggaru
\m 
\v 1 S uya, \add a\add* aytma iɛizzen d iɣřan, aqa kenniw d řefraḥet inu d ttaj inu, beddem xenni ammu nican di Siditneɣ, \add a\add* imɛizzen inu! \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt 1 Ts. 2:19. \x*
\m 
\v 2 Necc ttzawageɣ zeg Uwudiya d Sintici, maḥend ad imun array nsent di Siditneɣ.
\m 
\v 3 Ttzawageɣ ɛawed zzayek, \add a\add* amɛacar amtiqqi inu, maḥend ad tewced afus i tinni i ixeddmen akidi x ssibbet n \add tbarreḥt n\add* L’Injil, uřa ak-d Klimins d imsexxaren inu nneɣni, inni ismawen nsen yuran deg Wedlis \add ittwanḍen\add* n Tudart. \x ◘ \xo 4:3 \xt Uf. 32:32; Izhd. 69:29; Asa. 3:5; 20:12; 21:27. \x*
\m 
\v 4 Farḥem řebda di Siditneɣ, necc qqareɣ ɛawed: Farḥem! \x ◘ \xo 4:4 \xt 1 Ts. 5:16. \x*
\v 5 Ad yiři uwaḍeɛ nwem ittwassen ɣar iwdan marra. Siditneɣ aqa yudes. \x ◘ \xo 4:5 \xt 1 Kur. 10:11; Ɛbr. 10:25. \x*
\v 6 War kessim ca s wemnus x walu, maca ad yiři marra min tᵉttarem řebda ittwassen ɣar AREBBI s tẓaǧit d tkessit n řmeɛruf ak-d uqadi. \x ◘ \xo 4:6 \xt Izhd. 55:23; Mt. 6:25; 1 Tim. 6:8, 17; 1 Bṭ. 5:7. \x*
\v 7 Uca řehna n AREBBI i iɛdun marra řefhamet ad iḥḍa uřawen d ixarriṣen nwem di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt Yḥ. 14:27; Rum. 5:1; Afa. 2:14. \x*
\m 
\v 8 Ɣar uneggar, \add a\add* aytma, marra min iǧan d tidett, marra min iqquren, marra min iseggden, marra min izdigen, marra min iɛizzen, marra min ɣar iǧa řḥess aṣebḥan, u marra min ɣa isdaheǧen ccan d usemɣar, xarṣem dayes. \x ◘ \xo 4:8 \xt Rum. 13:13; 1 Ts. 4:3, 4, 5. \x*
\v 9 Min teɣrim u tqebřem, min tesřim u teẓrim zzayi, ggem t, uca AREBBI n řehna ad kiwem yiři!
\b
\m 
\v 10 Aqa farḥeɣ aṭṭas di Siditneɣ umi daywem iǧa wemnus maḥend ad ayi tᵉthillam, am mammec daywem t tuɣa \add qbeř\add*, maca war d as tufim mammec \add ad teggem\add*. \x ◘ \xo 4:10 \xt 2 Kur. 11:9. \x*
\v 11 War tt nniɣ, minzi necc ḥwajeɣ ca, minzi řemdeɣ ad qenɛeɣ mammec ma dd-tusa. \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt 1 Tim. 6:6. \x*
\v 12 Necc aqa ssneɣ umi qqaren ddeǧ, uca aqa ssneɣ umi qqaren afeyyeḍ. Mani ma u di marra aqa řemdeɣ, am di tyawant, am di řaẓ am deg ufeyyeḍ uřa di řeɣben. \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt 1 Kur. 4:11; 2 Kur. 11:27. \x*
\v 13 Qeddeɣ qaɛ zi Lmasiḥ wenni d ayi iwcin jjehd.
\v 14 Waxxa amenni mliḥ řami d ayi tewcim afus di řemḥayem inu.
\v 15 Tessnem ɛawed simant nwem, \add a\add* Ifilippiyyen, belli ɣar umezwaru n \add tbarreḥt n\add* Řexbar Aṣebḥan, umi dd-ffɣeɣ zi Makiduniya, uřa d ict n tmesmunt war teggi akidi řeḥsab x min wcin d min ksin, mɣir tenni nwem waha. \x ◘ \xo 4:15 \xt 2 Kur. 11:9. \x*
\v 16 Minzi ɛawed di Tissalunika tᵉssekkem ayi-dd min d ayi ittxeṣṣan, ijj n umur u ijj n umur nneɣni.
\v 17 War arezzuɣ ad dayi tewcem ca, maca arezzuɣ ad twesseɛ řɣiǧet nwem.
\v 18 Necc ṭṭfeɣ kuřci u ɣari kuřci s zzyada, aqa jjiwneɣ. Necc ksiɣ marra min d ayi dd-tᵉssekkem s ufus n Ipafruditus: ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen d ict n tɣarṣt yarḍan qibač i AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 4:18 \xt Ɛbr. 13:16. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 19 Maca AREBBI inu ad issyiwen marra min teḥdajem ɛlaḥsab agřa nnes deg uɛuǧi i iǧan n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.
\v 20 Aqa i AREBBI, Babatneɣ, ad ɣares yiři uɛuǧi d ccan i řebda qaɛ. Amin.
\b
\m 
\v 21 Seǧmem x kuř imqeddasen di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ s řehna.
\m Awmaten inni akidi, ttseǧamen xawem s řehna.
\m 
\v 22 Aqa marra imqeddasen ttseǧamen xawem s řehna, amezwaru inni iǧan zi taddart n qayṣar.
\m 
\v 23 Arḍa n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ ad yiři akidwem marra. Amin. 
